        "\n",
        "## Project Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "In this project, we compare two state-of-the-art transformer architectures for the task of sentiment classification:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **BERT (Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers):** A discriminative model that outputs class probabilities.\n",
        "2. **T5-Small (Text-to-Text Transfer Transformer):** A generative model that outputs text tokens directly (e.g., \"positive\" or \"negative\").\n",
        "\n",
        "We evaluate both models on the **Amazon Polarity** dataset, focusing on accuracy, F1-score, inference latency, and ethical considerations such as hallucination management for the generative approach.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
